query:
INSERT INTO price_history_locf (time, value)
                    SELECT s.time, t.value
                    FROM generate_series($1, $2, '1 second'::interval) AS s(time)
                    LEFT JOIN LATERAL (
                        SELECT value
                        FROM price_history
                        WHERE time <= s.time
                        ORDER BY time DESC
                        LIMIT 1
                    ) t ON true
